und may also invest in derivatives such as futures including among others interest rate futures swaps¬† currency interest rate credit default and total return forwards options and creditlinked notes the fund is nondiversified under the investment company act of  as amended and may invest a larger percentage of its assets in fewer¬† issuers than diversified funds download risks equity funds are primarily subject to all the investment risks associated with underlying stocks stocks have shown greater growth potential than other types of securities but they have also shown greater volatility and risk of loss investments made in small or midcap stocks are generally more volatile and subject to greater risk investments made in foreign or emerging markets are subject to special risks that are not normally associated with domestic investment including possible adverse currency fluctuations and political social and economic risks there can be no assurance that any fund will achieve its objective fixed income funds are primarily subject to all the investment risks associated with the underlying bonds and other fixedincome securities bonds are subject to interest rate and credit risk as interest rates rise the value of a bond fund can go down and an investor can lose principal investments made in high yield bonds are subject to greater volatility and potential loss of principal investments made in foreign and emerging market bonds are subject to special risks that are not normally associated with domestic investment including possible adverse currency fluctuations and political social and economic risks there can be no assurance that any fund will achieve its objective the mercer core fixed income fund mercer opportunistic fixed income fund and the mercer global low volatility equity fund may invest in more aggressive investments such as derivatives futures options swaps all of which may cause greater volatility and less liquidity derivatives are more sensitive to changes in market conditions and may amplify risks the mercer global low volatility equity fund relies on quantitative models techniques and risk analyses employed by the subadvisers which is designed to enhance potential return but if an error occurs it could result in losses to the fund please carefully consider the funds investment objectives risks charges and expenses before investing for this and other information write mercer investment management inc  high street boston ma  attn client services for a free prospectus read it carefully before you invest or send money mercer funds are offered by prospectus only these webpages are for us persons only products and services contained on these webpages may not be available for residents of other jurisdictions persons for whom such restrictions apply must not access these webpages the information in these webpages does not constitute legal tax or financial advice nor should any investment or any other decisions be made solely on the information contained herein you should consult an attorney tax professional or other qualified expert regarding your specific situation and circumstances services in the us are provided by mercer investment management inc mercer funds distributor the mercer funds are distributed by mgi funds distributors llc berwyn pa not affiliated with mercer investment management inc ¬† countries mgi funds plc germany netherlands norway portugal sweden uk us contact us send us your question terms of use ¬†¬† privacy the information contained in this website is for information purposes only it should not be taken in any way as advice it should not be relied upon as an offer to purchase or sell any of the products that are discussed  mercer llc all rights reserved mercer  make tomorrow today mercer  make tomorrow today we use cookies to improve your experience¬† by using our site you agree that we can place cookies on your device please see our¬†privacy policy for details ok all choose your location country sites a